x; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; text-align: left; padding-top: 4px; border-collapse: separate; width: 340px;">Ride-share services such as Uber are, literally, taking off. The main reason so many people are eager to transport strangers to and fro: to tackle debt. <a target="_blank" style="box-sizing: content-box; color: rgb(0, 50, 104); text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.creditcards.com/credit-card-news/ride-share-driver-pay-down-debt-1267.php/?a_aid=e38bc565">More...</a><br></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="width: 340px;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td style="clear: both; box-sizing: content-box; padding-top: 6px; padding-bottom: 6px; border-collapse: separate; width: 340px; overflow: visible;"><table style="width: 340px;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td style="position: relative; clear: both; overflow: visible; box-sizing: content-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1em; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; text-align: left; padding: 0px; border-collapse: separate; width: 340px;"><a target="_blank" style="box-sizing: content-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.creditcards.com/credit-card-news/8-bankruptcy-myths-1282.php/?a_aid=e38bc565">8 myths surrounding bankruptcy</a><br></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="width: 340px;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td style="position: relative; clear: both; overflow: visible; box-sizing: content-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; text-align: left; padding-top: 4px; border-collapse: separate; width: 340px;">Filing for bankruptcy is a huge financial step, and many jump in with misconceptions of what it will and won't do. Here are eight things you may have heard about bankruptcy that may not be necessarily true. <a target="_blank" style="box-sizing: content-box; color: rgb(0, 50, 104); text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.creditcards.com/credit-card-news/8-bankruptcy-myths-1282.php/?a_aid=e38bc565">More...</a><br></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>


                                            </td>
